reviewText:
My son and daughter loved so much. Watched over and over again.
I recommend this DVD to everyone . Thank you
My 3 and 5 year-old grandchildren are enthralled by this DVD and I think it is a hoot also. It is a good value.
A must read, especially in the voice of an old man from Brooklyn.
The kids at school love them
Nice follow up to the Mo Willems stories
Bought for grandchild and she loved it.
My 4 year old son thinks the pigeon books are hysterical.  He is in love with any book we read by Mo Willems.
what is there not to like about the pigeon. Good video, prefer thebooks
I love Mo Willems! His books are great for children. I will use these videos in my Kindergarten classroom every year.
